@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "FAQ";
}

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

        <div class="list-group">
            <a class="list-group-item" href="#question1" style="display:block;">Question 1: What products do you sell on this website?</a>
            <a class="list-group-item" href="#question2" style="display:block;">Question 2: Does MRJ commerce have a return policy?</a>
            <a class="list-group-item" href="#question3" style="display:block;">Question 3: What shipping options does MRJ Commerce offer?</a>
            <a class="list-group-item" href="#question4" style="display:block;">Question 4: How can I sell my own clothing items on MRJ Commerce?</a>
            <a class="list-group-item" href="#question5" style="display:block;">Question 5: How do I track my order?</a>
            <a class="list-group-item" href="#question6" style="display:block;">Question 6: Can I buy clothing items as gifts for special occasions?</a>
            <a class="list-group-item" href="#question7" style="display:block;">Question 7: Is there a limit to the number of products I can sell per month on MRJ Commerce?</a>
            <a class="list-group-item" href="#question8" style="display:block;">Question 8: How do I contact customer support if I have any issues or questions?</a>
            <a class="list-group-item" href="#question9" style="display:block;">Question 9: Are there any fees for buying products on MRJ Commerce?</a>
            <a class="list-group-item" href="#question10" style="display:block;">Question 10: Is MRJ Commerce available on mobile devices?</a>
        </div>

        <br />
        <!-- Questions and answers -->
        <dl class="list-group">
            <dt id="question1" class="list-group-item">Question 1: What products do you sell on the this website? </dt>
            <dd>
                <br />
                MRJ commerce sells all kinds of clothing products (shirts, shoes, shorts etc), suitable for various occasions and weather conditions. TEST
            </dd>
            <br />

            <dt id="question2" class="list-group-item">Question 2: Does MRJ commerce have a return policy?</dt>
            <dd>
                <br />
                MRJ Commerce offers a hassle-free return policy for most items within 30 days of purchase,
                as long as the items are in their original condition.
                Please see our Return Policy page for more information and instructions on how to initiate a return.
            </dd>
            <br />

            <dt id="question3" class="list-group-item">Question 3: What shipping options does MRJ Commerce offer?</dt>
            <dd>
                <br />
                We provide flexible shipping options, partnering with multiple carriers such as USPS, UPS, and FedEx. Customers can choose from various shipping tiers, including standard, expedited, and express shipping, depending on their needs.
            </dd>
            <br />

            <dt id="question4" class="list-group-item">Question 4: How can I sell my own clothing items on MRJ Commerce?</dt>
            <dd>
                <br />
                MRJ Commerce allows users to sell their clothing items on our platform through our brokerage model, which includes auction and transaction brokers. You can list your items for sale or auction, and MRJ Commerce will handle the platform and advertisement for your products.
            </dd>
            <br />

            <dt id="question5" class="list-group-item">Question 5: How do I track my order?</dt>
            <dd>
                <br />
                Once your order has been shipped, you will receive a confirmation email with a tracking number. You can use this number to track your package through the carrier's website or the MR                J Commerce order tracking page.
            </dd>
            <br />

            <dt id="question6" class="list-group-item">Question 6: Can I buy clothing items as gifts for special occasions?</dt>
            <dd>
                <br />
                Absolutely! MRJ Commerce offers great suggestions for gifts suitable for various occasions, such as Christmas, Birthdays, Mother's and Father's Day, and Valentine's Day. Look out for special deals and promotions during these periods.
            </dd>
            <br />

            <dt id="question7" class="list-group-item">Question 7: Is there a limit to the number of products I can sell per month on MRJ Commerce?</dt>
            <dd>
                <br />
                Yes, there is a limit to the number of products you can sell per month. Once you reach that limit, you will need to pay additional fees for any additional items listed within the same month. Please refer to our Seller Fees page for more information on these limits and fees.
            </dd>
            <br />

            <dt id="question8" class="list-group-item">Question 8: How do I contact customer support if I have any issues or questions?</dt>
            <dd>
                <br />
                Our customer support team is available to assist you with any questions or concerns. You can reach us by phone at 904-906-907 or via email at support@mrjcommerce.com. You can also chat with us using our live chat feature.
            </dd>
            <br />

            <dt id="question9" class="list-group-item">Question 9: Are there any fees for buying products on MRJ Commerce?</dt>
            <dd>
                <br />
                There are no additional fees for buying products on MRJ Commerce, aside from the product price and applicable shipping costs. However, please note that any taxes or customs fees, if applicable, are the responsibility of the buyer.
            </dd>
            <br />

            <dt id="question10" class="list-group-item">Question 10: Is MRJ Commerce available on mobile devices?</dt>
            <dd>
                <br />
                Yes, MRJ Commerce is available on both desktop and mobile devices, offering a seamless shopping experience for customers on the go. Access our website through your mobile browser or download our mobile app for even more convenience.
            </dd>
            <br />
        </dl>
    </div>
</body>
